high_descs: Take a right, walk to the toilet and face the back of the toilet.
Pick up the tube from the back of the toilet.
Turn around and face the cabinets below the sink.
Open the cabinet door on the right side below the right sink, place the tube in the cabinet, and shut the door.
Walk to the right side of the right sink.
Pick up the tube from the right side of the sink.
Move away from the sink to look at the cabinet below the sink.
Open the cabinet door on the right side, place the tube in the cabinet to the right of the first tube, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To move two tubes to the cabinet below the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the counter, then turn right and walk up to the wall, turn right again to face the toilet.
Pick up the toilet paper tube off of the toilet tank.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right to face the counter.
Open the lower right cabinet door below the counter and put the toilet paper tube inside, then close the.
Walk over to the right side of the sink counter.
Pick up the cardboard toilet paper tube off of the counter.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the toilet and turn around to face the counter.
Open the lower right cabinet door below the counter and put the toilet paper tube inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Move two toilet paper tubes into a cabinet.

high_descs: Go to the right, walk towards the cabinet, turn right to go to the toilet and face the left side of the toilet.
Pick up an empty toilet paper roll on the water tank.
Turn around and go to the cabinet under the sink.
Open the cabinet, put the empty toilet paper roll in it and close the cabinet.
Look to the sink on top of the cabinet.
Pick up another toilet paper roll near the sink.
Go back to the cabinet under the sink.
Open the cabinet, put the other empty toilet paper roll in the cabinet and close it.
anns.task_desc: Store 2 empty toilet paper rolls in the cabinet under the sink that is the closest to the toilet.
